Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.37,0:22:17.21,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Saka no tochuu de hitori furi muku
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.37,0:22:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,While climbing up the hill, one turns around and looks
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.20,0:22:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though there was not a soul in sight
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.20,0:22:24.53,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Dare mo inai no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.41,0:22:33.03,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Hidamari no naka nayami mo shirazu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.41,0:22:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,In the sunny spot, blissfully oblivious of worries
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.17,0:22:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So we spent days when you were still alive
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.17,0:22:42.05,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Ikiteita ano hi
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.55,0:22:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why is it only when one loses something,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.55,0:22:50.23,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Nee hito wa itsumo nani ka nakushita toki ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.10,0:22:58.54,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Ari no mama no jibun ni kidzuku no
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.10,0:22:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He gets to perceive what was actually going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.54,0:23:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I wonder if you can hear me \Neven while you're not here anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.54,0:23:06.55,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Nee ima wa inai anata kikoeru kashira
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.09,0:23:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So I made a promise to carry on living my own way, \Ntherefore you must also, even if for an eternity,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.09,0:23:17.67,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Watashi rashiku ikite yuku to yakusoku suru kara anata wa itsumade mo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.06,0:23:21.23,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Miteite ne
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.06,0:23:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep looking after me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.18,0:23:25.14,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Tooku kara
