Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.46,0:01:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,New York! New York! New York!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.89,0:01:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We got to use the entire first day for recreation!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.37,0:01:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to see the Statue Of Liberty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.33,0:01:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go through every sightseeing course \Nin my guidebook!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.68,0:01:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, seeing it yourself \Nis nothing like hearing about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And not just seeing...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.94,0:01:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I have trod my first, yet so historically important \Nfor my life, step on the American soil.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.93,0:01:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I just regret Coach is not here with us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:01:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach Munakata, \Nget discharged soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.99,0:02:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Please reunite with us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:09.83,Sign,,0,0,0,,Mourning
