Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.36,0:02:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahoy, Maki! \NAre you doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, my New York life starts!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:03:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope back in Japan, \NMr. Sun is benevolent to everyone as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.79,0:03:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyhow, the prime unusual thing about here \Nis how tremendously king size everything is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,People and cities alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the hotel we've stopped in is... \NGuess what, 80 floors high!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone like Maki would probably go "Kyaaa!" and faint \Nby just looking down from the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, our team of young Japanese players \Nfrom this hotel on New York's 8th avenue,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,has to attend tennis court every day \Nas a part of our practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.70,0:03:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, in this tour we'll compete \Nnot just with players from America,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but from Britain, France, and Australia as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.83,0:03:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,For each of participating young player teams, \Nthis is their first trial of strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.39,0:03:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Tournament format matches \Nare synthesized with practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.10,0:03:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This time Hiromi is surely giving it her best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.10,0:03:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it must be Bianca from France.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.68,0:04:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Still in high school, on All-France's Open, \Nshe made it to the final selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty players who'd qualify effortlessly as a pro \Nare all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How much tension!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.57,0:04:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,One set. Will you do me this honor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Todo, should we probably start too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Three-set as usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.55,0:04:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlimited deathmatch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Oka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a person seeking to meet you. \NCould you come to the clubhouse for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Warmest greetings, Miss Hiromi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You know who he is, Oka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I often see him in magazines. \NA famous Australian tennis coach...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, it is Mister Reynolds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Ms. Hiromi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.19,0:05:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Very glad, Mr. Reynolds!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes without saying, Reynolds family includes \Na bunch of young players from Australia -
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Angie Reynolds \Nand of course, Eddy Reynolds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.73,0:05:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He became famous for bringing up those siblings \Nnot just as a father would, but as a coach as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This time as well, Angie and Eddy keep him company, \Nparticipating as a part of Australian team.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Mr. Reynolds resigned as Australian team's coach \Ntoday, with proposition to become your coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.02,0:05:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I already have my own regular coach. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach Munakata isn't it? \NHiromi's coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you see, he's not here. \NHe is in Japan now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But Coach Munakata will soon join us too. Therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.31,0:05:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.66,0:06:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It was actually Coach Munakata \Nwho put forward this idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he's coming late, \Nhe asked Mr. Reynolds to coach you until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You may not be aware of that, but Mr. Reynolds has been Munakata's pal ever since they were players themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach Munakata's request?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mister Reynolds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So is it OK now, Ms. Hiromi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Well then, until Coach Munakata joins us, \Nplease take care of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,OK! Let's both do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:06:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hear out my proposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I think Munakata \Nwould have proposed it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Munakata's death... For some while, \NI want you to conceal that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She is now left to walk a long road \Nall alone and away from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,At such a moment, what may happen, \Nshould that fact come to light?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.90,0:07:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think anyone can say for certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Oka should now \Ncarry forth that tennis Munakata entrusted her with.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's now more than ever important for her \Nto keep going undisturbed through that tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.07,0:07:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, at least until Oka Hiromi returns to Japan,\NI want you to hold that fact in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand it perfectly, Daigo. \NI will do everything I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't leak to any mass-media. I'll see to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.50,0:07:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you kindly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.18,0:07:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Even by going to New York, I won't help you one bit. \NI understand that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, Oka, even if I can't be of any service to you, \NI just want to be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If the worst case scenario hits you after all, \Nat least I would be there to say a word of consolation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Hiromi!\NWatch the ball more closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In just three years of tennis, such a play... \NSuch power!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.33,0:08:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And that fighting spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Munakata really have to leave behind such a miracle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a fervor for ball...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just for Munakata, but for the tennis of the world, \Nwe cannot let her passion burn out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going, Hiromi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.86,0:08:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.29,0:08:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:08:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Oka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.65,0:09:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Muster all the strength you believe you have \Nand hit that ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice, Hiromi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And not just for practice, \Nbut for an actual match too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not about techniques, but the spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.71,0:09:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget your personality and engrave it! \NOn the ball! The ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mr. Reynolds has been attached to Oka as coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's all alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,With exception of Mr. Reynolds, \NI haven't told anyone about Coach Munakata.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.54,0:09:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.28,0:09:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Manager, don't you think it's strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,One week... No, even if he arrives 2 weeks late, \Nall 3 previous years, he has been raising Oka{/ bringing up/ nurturing Oka} himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.39,0:10:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You think Coach Munakata would suddenly entrust \Na player so important to him to some other coach like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.82,0:10:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say? \NI can't quite grasp your point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I know what times Coach Munakata and Oka \Nbeen through together,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,what sufferings endured, \Nwhat walls climbed over, I'm saying that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.87,0:10:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No chance! For him to willingly entrust Oka \Nto a coach other than himself in this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Never before there has been a chance for such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If the things are really this way, then... Then!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.36,0:10:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You are overthinking, Todo.\NNothing particular happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In Japan, nothing changed either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the Japan's team captain, \Nand it's unbecoming of captain to panic like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I overheard what you said just before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Your call to management in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,"I haven't told about Coach Munakata \Nto anyone except Mr. Reynolds."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.38,0:10:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me know the truth, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo, you'll have to believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oy! There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My, only you bothered to come greet me? \NI'm so lonesome! {I'm so tempted to write "I'll never forgive the Japanese!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.21,0:11:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozaki wanted to come too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I assured him I'd manage alone... \NThen locked in his room just in case!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hurry up \Nand show me the way to hotel already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.16,0:11:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't we both a bit starvey?{he is using a childish playful proverb here}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.02,0:11:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it you wanted to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.32,0:11:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,When did Coach pass away?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot, Munakata is still undergoing \Na thorough checkup.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We are friends, aren't we?! \NCan't you tell me frankly?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't... anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:11:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the truth about his condition! \NHis true condition, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Spit it out, Chiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.23,0:12:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Clearly and straightforwardly!{/ Enunciate it with your mouth!}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiba, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.89,0:12:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,His farewell{/ final} words are{/ were}\N"Oka, aim for the ace!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,January 15, at 6:37 pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,As your plane was taking off from Japanese soil, \Nhe took his last breath.{don't get the second part, maybe lit would rather be "so I'm told" or "he said that"}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.79,0:12:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,First round matchups finally arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Along with you, players from 4 more countries \Ntake part in this tournament.{he rather says just "4 countries participate" but that contradicts what Oka said earlier}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.81,0:12:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The underlying idea is not to promote inter-country rivalry spirit or team cohesion spirit.{/ is not to compete between countries or between team members.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.81,0:13:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, developing players' techniques case by case \Nis the main objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.03,0:13:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We want you to learn the most you can \Nfrom fighting foreign players.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,For Japanese Tennis Association, these matches will serve \Na gauge of Japan's level of ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.67,0:13:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, those matches should lay foundation \Nfor determining our objectives hereafter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you all a fair wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:20.04,Sign,,0,0,0,,Oka Hiromi (JP) \NMaria Young (US)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.89,0:13:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria Young?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maria Young...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The most prominent pupil of Lady King, \Nsaid to be a world-class genius player!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria Young will fight me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka, I was 6 when I first clasped the racket.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.66,0:13:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then and to this day, \Nmy dad is my only coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,On dad's recommendation, I worked \Nwith countless amazing coaches of outstanding abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.86,0:14:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,However, with every new coach I met, \NI couldn't help coming to the same conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.46,0:14:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Although these days he can no longer teach me \Na single thing about techniques or theory, dad is still...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.15,0:14:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to me, the only possible coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not the only one feeling this way - \Noceans away from her coach, alone in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep up the good work and don't lose the spirits. \NYou do, and so will I.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.54,0:14:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't pull that bitter face when looking at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of us have to remain strong no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.98,0:14:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Madame{fuck fuck fuck fuck fuck}. \NBut I just cannot be as strong as you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm uneasy, and I don't know how to help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm letting Coach Reynolds down, \Nbut I just can't focus on the practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach, please come sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach! Coach Munakata!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach, is your health getting better?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.09,0:15:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned today that in the first round of tournament, \NI'm getting put up against Maria Young.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But Coach, without you here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... In Japan, it should be very early morning. \NIt feels a bit awkward to dial the hospital now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria Young?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.21,0:15:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,From the get-go{/ very first shot}, you're put up \Nagainst such a mighty target{guess}! Well, aren't you lucky?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ding-dong!{/ Ping-pong! / Bingo!} Maki, you think so too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, I bet Coach \Nwill be even more than me delighted to get this!{guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of, how is Coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know much myself, \Nbut I heard he is getting discharged any day now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.13,0:15:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Finally! \NThen, you know when Coach departs?{/ heads here?; I wan't to make this word "departs" because Oka cluelessly is using it in it's primary sense and Maki understands in secondary, which is "die"}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Maki... Hey, Maki, you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Very soon, they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, international calls are expensive, \Nso I'm hanging up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep doing your best! \NBecause I'll be rooting for you firmly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanging up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best, Hiromi...\NYour best!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.86,0:16:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that? \NWeirdo Maki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm never calling you again in that case!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Gonna go have a run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thought I'd go run to sleep better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had the same thought as Todo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:17:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Really having a hard time falling asleep. \NI guess it's jet lag...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna run together?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! With pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best against Maria Young.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.93,0:17:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how far away, \NMunakata never stops watching over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't it always been this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.66,0:17:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go easy on her, Oka. \NWith all might!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.86,0:17:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. How about we run to Central Park and back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.70,0:17:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay strong, Oka. Strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.22,0:17:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm coming so late, Papa, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really late, Angie. \NI thought you aren't coming at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I miss such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,For her sake, Papa even resigned as our coach. \NIt's Hiromi Oka's match.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:18:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see what resistance can she put up \Nagainst Maria Young.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't miss it, by all means!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that so, Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The best of the three set match!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.28,0:18:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka's service. Play!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.10,0:18:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,15-0.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Service ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.82,0:18:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Spectacular!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fast ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.01,0:18:34.43,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,I throw open the door to my heart because we're starting
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice serve there, Oka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:42.07,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Have been hobbling in zigzags but it's about time I start walking steadily!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.81,0:18:47.20,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,You discover yourself anew, youth is always an eventful season!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,30-0.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.66,0:18:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Look closely at her moves, \Nthen hit where it hurts!{guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:53.88,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,You know what to do - don't stop, young heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,40-0.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Step boldly ahead and hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:19:07.70,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,But your answer has passed me by, wind is carrying it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.26,0:19:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Game! 1-0, Oka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.40,0:19:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing! It's a love-game!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:14.17,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,It's my endless dreaming still fresh in my memory
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:20.60,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,It's like stepping on a marsh countless times to find a solid path
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.66,0:19:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:27.10,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,It's my endless dreaming, so I keep on walking
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:34.32,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Towards the blessed season of me and you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost unbelievable, Papa! \NThis match is so one-sided!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Maria is out of form?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wrong. \NIt's Hiromi's form that is so fearsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,To the point of nullifying Maria's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.64,0:19:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason, I have this sensation - my body is so light, \NI can move exactly the way Coach taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.97,0:19:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This sensation of pure and unobstructed perception...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.54,0:20:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A player endowed with outstanding potential
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.89,0:20:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly hits her prime{/ starts riding the waves of good} form one of these days, \Nmaking progress by leaps and bounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly, for Hiromi, that time is right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.65,0:20:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,However... The higher peaks she reaches while here, \Nwhen she finds out about Munakata's death,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the more bottomless will be her despair{/ devastation} of a player!{/ the higher are the chances she'll be completely ruined / crushed / lost as a player.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.87,0:20:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,40-15!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's match point now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.82,0:20:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I am... I am going to lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.78,0:20:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The Great Maria Young is losing this so pitifully?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.23,0:20:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that cannot be true. \NRight, I must be seeing a bad dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.07,0:20:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.86,0:21:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only way... \NThe only way I'd ever lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.34,0:21:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Game set!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.71,0:21:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Match won by Hiromi Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.68,0:21:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Won...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Won it, Coach!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.25,0:21:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin, you used to always have Oka on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.91,0:21:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me to make it OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.34,0:21:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Whichever hell Oka Hiromi lands into after this, \NI will... I will make sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.86,0:23:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Aikawa Maki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.66,0:23:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's terrible, everyone finds out about Coach Munakata!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.99,0:23:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame Butterfly and Ozaki too...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.05,0:23:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi is the only one to remain ignorant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.88,0:23:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite that, she's knitting \Na muffler for Coach, our Hiromi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.95,0:23:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But until the tour is over, \NHiromi must not, by all means, find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.89,0:23:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lose, Hiromi!\NEverybody's rooting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.38,0:24:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode: \NNew York Melancholy
